Class FacultyPane

  • java.lang.Object
    • view.FacultyPane

  • public class FacultyPane
extends java.lang.Object
    FacultyPane class builds GridPane using JavaFX that will allow the user to add Faculty Objects to the courseList array. The FacultyPane will also be able to display all the faculty that have been created.
    Author:
    Caio Eugenio
